    <item>
      <title>memoiR</title>
      <link>https://ericmarcon.github.io/en/software/memoir/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://ericmarcon.github.io/en/software/memoir/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;memoiR&lt;/em&gt; is an R package that provides templates to publish well-formatted documents both in HTML and PDF formats. Documents can be produced locally or hosted on GitHub, where GitHub actions can update the published documents continuously.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Long documents are the main purpose of this package. Along with a GitBook version to be read online, their PDF version based on the LaTeX class memoir can be highly customized.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Functions are provided to make the publication of the documents on GitHub very easy, including their continuous integration.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
